ORIGIN '../guienv';
LIB_ITEM 'guienv';
BODY 'private/rasteraddsbody';
(* INCLUDE '../raster'; *)

-- guienvlib: attributes --
iconResource: pixmap
  (# <<SLOT pixmapLib: attributes>>;
     loadById:
       (# id: @integer;
       enter id
       do ...
       #);
  #);

bitmapResource: pixmap
  (# <<SLOT pixmapLib2: attributes>>;
     loadById:
       (# id: @integer;
          success: @boolean;
       enter id
       ...
       exit success
       #);
     loadByName:
       (# name: ^text;
          success: @boolean;
       enter name[]
       ...
       exit success
       #);
  #)
